data.description: This beautifully updated condo is located in Ghent Square with many amenities including a pool, playground, clubhouse, private parking, tennis and grounds maintenance. The kitchen opens up to the dining and living room filled with natural light and a wood burning fireplace. Step outside to the patio that overlooks the scenic Mowbray Arch. Large bedrooms and an updated gorgeous bathroom make this condo a one of a kind find in Ghent. Not to mention a new HVAC, water heater, and kitchen cabinets, and appliances! Close by to shopping, restaurants, Chrysler Museum, NEON Art District, Harrison Opera House and so much more!
